Name: SKYRAID
About the game: SKYRAID is a 6 vs 6 online mulitplayer game of conquest. Engage in high speed aerial combat like you've never experienced it before, with a top-down camera angle, skill-based movement and combat mechanics, advanced guided weaponry and emergency countermeasures. Escort airborne forces deep into enemy territory to destroy emplacements, ships, drones, helicopters, and more. Game Features Online Multiplayer for up to 6v6 with objectives and creeps Skill-based gameplay and risk-vs-reward equipment progression Multiple generations of iconic fighters for you to collect and pilot from ranging from WWII propellers to modern multirole jets. (At least 25 are planned for the full release) Start with props and upgrade your way to jets over the course of a single match Huge variety of weapons and countermeasures to engage your enemies with 'Kill-Tree' kill-streak skill-tree to snowball your power in battle Unique and vibrant art style Novice / Expert control modes and Controller Support Unlocked Framerate Resolution independent render scaling
